summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twenty-fourth Avenue Northwest, from West 65th Street to West 75th Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 18680, creating Local Improvement District No. 1781 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
